    "description": {
      "value": "<p>To use this technique, you must have a Speed Rank of 4 or higher active. You move forward up to 30 ft, making a series of extremely fast and subtle attacks. You can make a single melee attack against up to one creature per level inside the area (maximum 15).<br><br>These attacks cannot score a critical hit, and apply a number of sneak attack dice up to your Intelligence modifier (maximum 3d6). You do not provoke attacks of opportunity while moving this way.</p>\n\n\n\n",
